cnoremap <silent> <M-k> <Esc>:call NavigateUp(0)<CR>
cnoremap <silent> <M-l> <Esc>:call NavigateRight(0)<CR>
cnoremap <silent> <M-\> <Esc>:call NavigatePrevious(0)<CR>

